main event: A pilot in an F-86 aircraft observed a green conical shaped light overtaking a F-80 aircraft in Pyongtaek, Korea.
interesting points: The observation occurred at 2025 GMT and lasted for 3 seconds, The object was on a course parallel to the F-80, The light was described as green and conical in shape, The source of the report is military, and the conclusion was insufficient data for evaluation.
